# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Frontend (Vite) — shipped in the browser, must be public-safe
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_SUPABASE_URL="https://YOUR-PROJECT-REF.supabase.co"
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY"
VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID="YOUR-PROJECT-REF"

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Supabase Edge Functions — set via `supabase secrets set ...`
# NEVER ship these to the browser. Do not commit.
#
# Required by every pipeline stage:
#   SUPABASE_URL                  (auto-injected in Supabase runtime)
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY     (auto-injected in Supabase runtime)
#   LOVABLE_API_KEY               — set manually; token for the Lovable AI gateway
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Example (for local `supabase functions serve`):
# SUPABASE_URL="https://YOUR-PROJECT-REF.supabase.co"
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY="YOUR_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY"
# LOVABLE_API_KEY="lv_..."
